			<script type="text/javascript">
			function logar() {
				if( $("#login").val() == "" ||  $("#login").val() == null ){
					$("#loginAviso").fadeIn(3000,function(){
									$("#loginAviso").html("Por Favor digite um login");
					});
				}
				if( $("#senha").val() == "" ||  $("#senha").val() == null ){
					$("#senhaAviso").html("Por Favor digite uma senha");
				}
				if( $("#login").val() != "" && $("#senha").val()!= "" ){
					$.post("/" + "lib/CallClassFunction.php",
					{
						clazz: "Login", func: "realizarLogin",
						login: $('#login').val(),
						senha: $('#senha').val()
					}, {}, "json"
					).success(
						function(r) {
										location.reload(true)
						}
					 )
					 .fail(
						 function(f){
							 $("#modalLoginError").html("Login e/ou Senha inválidos");
						 }
					);
				}
			}
			$("#login").on("click",function(){
				$("#loginAviso").html("");
				$("#modalLoginError").html("");
			});
			$("#senha").on("click",function(){
				$("#senhaAviso").html("");
				$("#modalLoginError").html("");
			});
			$('#modalLogin').on('hidden.bs.modal', function () {
				$("#loginAviso").html("");
				$("#senhaAviso").html("");
				$("#modalLoginError").html("");
			})

			function logout() {
				$.post("/" + "lib/CallClassFunction.php",
				{
					clazz: "Login", func: "realizarLogout"
				}, {}, "json"
				).success(
					function(r) {
						location.reload(true)
					}
				)
			}
			</script>

			<script type='text/javascript'>
			(function($){
				$(document).ready(function(){
					$('ul.dropdown-menu [data-toggle=dropdown]').on('click', function(event) {
						event.preventDefault();
						event.stopPropagation();
						$(this).parent().siblings().removeClass('open');
						$(this).parent().toggleClass('open');
					});

					//carrega o conteudo do item contatos apenas quando o usuario clica no botao
					$('#modalContato').on('show.bs.modal', function (event) {
						var modal = $(this);
						var texto = ''
						+ '<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">'
						+ '	<tr>'
						+ '		<td width="60%">'
						+ '			<iframe src="/pagina/contatoMapa.html" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" height="380" width="100%"></iframe>'
						+ '		</td>'
						+ '		<td width="2%">&nbsp;</td>'
						+ '		<td width="63%" valign="top">Ministério da Saúde<br />'
						+ '			Esplanada dos Ministérios Bloco G<br />'
						+ '			Brasília-DF / CEP: 70058-900 <br />'
						+ '			Telefone: +51 (61) 3315-7964 <br />'

					$('#modalExpediente').on('show.bs.modal', function (event) {
						var modal = $(this);
						var p = "/pagina/expediente.php";
						$.ajax(p).done(function(texto) {
							modal.find('.modal-body').html(texto);
						});
					});

						var modal = $(this);

					$('map').imageMapResize();
				});
			})(jQuery);
